[SN]TITLE[SN]
The 999 call by murderer who killed friend with claw hammer

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Louis Maguire has been jailed for 17 years for the murder of a man who was beaten to death with a claw hammer in north Belfast.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
30 November 2016 Last updated at 14:58 GMT
Following the sentencing, police released a recording of a 999 call which Maguire made after carrying out the murder, in which he claimed to police that he had returned home and found Mr Ferguson badly injured in his house.
